title: Fly into the east side of the UK landing at the updated Humberside Airport (EGNJ)
description:
Humberside Airport (EGNJ) has been updated in MSFS, enhancing the default scenery with a wealth of details. The update encompasses both sides of the airport and introduces various static scenery elements.
